name: Bacchanal Flat Notecard with Free US Shipping
description:
This extraordinary handmade note card is printed from a high resolution scan of my finished needlepoint piece. This offers a 3D texture to the card.

The note card is blank on the other side and each one is printed on an inkjet printer and hand cut by me.

They are printed using archival inks on 100% cotton rag 300gsm (140lb) paper.

Each card is sized 5.75" x 5.75" and comes with a square envelope and a not your grandmas needlepoint sticker.
